chara.textHome: The merriest of seasons greetings to all!
A spell of happiness for the day shall@be cast upon those fortunate enough@to meet Miss Santa.
Good morning.@The air is still quite chilly outside and@yet I must rise at this early hour.
Miss Santa must be a good role model@for the children.
Word of a restaurant that prepares@Christmas-themed Chinese dishes@upon request has reached my ears...
Just what could they be?@My interest has been piqued...
I am awaiting Tsukasa's arrival.
She's quite busy and has been late@in the past. However, I haven't the@slightest doubt that she will come.
I have but one wish for Santa before@I turn in for the night...
to see Tsukasa again tomorrow.
I have revered this outfit since@I was quite little.
I mean, Miss Santa can cast magic@that brings happiness to all children!
The time has come for Tsukasa and me@to depart to eliminate Witches.
Miss Santa shall cast her magic to dispose@of this threat and protect the children!
I witnessed a copy of Alina...
my apologies,@Miss Alina dressed in a Christmas outfit@within the Mirrors Labyrinth...
Whatever could it mean?
Miss Santa came to my rescue@when I had become lost many years ago...
The only explanation I could fathom@was that she had used magic.
I prepared this outfit specifically to attend@a Christmas party with Tsukasa.
I'm very much looking forward to it.
One of Sankyoya's signature@Christmas sweets, chilled matcha cake,@is to be made available soon...
How wonderful it would be@to have one with Tsukasa.
There are those even among Magical Girls@who cannot feel holiday cheer...
As Miss Santa, I would love to bestow them@with happiness.
My family is well aware that I shall be@attending a Christmas party,
but I have naturally kept my intent@to see Tsukasa a secret from them.
My favorite accessory is@this ribbon with bells.
It has the same bells that adorn Tsukasa's.
While I don't consider myself lacking@in friends, the only one with whom@I exchange presents is Tsukasa...
Ah, perhaps I am short on friends after all?
I've only just realized that,@with a change in color scheme, @the fur adorning Mifuyu's Magical Girl form
could look very similar to that of Miss Santa!
What...? I-it suits me, does it?
...Being told that so formally@is slightly embarrassing...
